rontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_cpu_usage_rate", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我已经完成了故障时间窗口内的初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"adservice--stress\",\n    \"stress\",\n    \"Byteman\",\n    \"StressHelper\",\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"Transformer\",\n    \"TriggerThread\",\n    \"Rule.execute\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman chaos injection stress testing causing service instability\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService--stress-1749255024 execute() 和 Rule.execute called for AdService--stress-1749255024 高频出现，表明正在进行压力测试注入\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent startup failure and InvocationTargetException\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! 和 Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException 表明Byteman代理启动失败\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple stress threads creation and execution\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Creating thread AdService--stress-1749255024X, Starting thread AdService--stress-1749255024X, Running thread AdService--stress-1749255024X 显示多个压力测试线程被创建和执行\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **故障类型**：这是一次有意的混沌工程测试（Chaos Engineering），而非意外故障\n2. **影响范围**：所有3个adservice实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）都受到影响\n3. **故障模式**：Byteman工具被用于注入压力测试规则（AdService--stress-1749255024）\n4. **症状表现**：高频的stress规则执行，伴随代理启动失败和反射调用异常\n\n**建议后续步骤**：\n- 确认这是否为预期的混沌测试\n- 检查Byteman配置和压力测试参数\n- 监控adservice的性能指标以评估测试影响程度\n- 验证测试完成后服务是否恢复正常", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的调用链数据，我已完成对故障时间窗口的初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作HGET异常延迟：正常1.55ms，异常35.22s（延迟倍数22.7倍）；HMSET操作正常1.36ms，异常12.32s（延迟倍数9.1倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend调用AdService异常延迟：正常5.4-5.5s，异常30.2-38.1s（延迟倍数5.5-6.9倍），出现次数38次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkout调用CartService异常延迟：正常2.2-2.4s，异常8.2-14.6s（延迟倍数3.4-6.0倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkout调用ShippingService异常延迟：正常0.2-0.2s，异常0.5-1.6s（延迟倍数2.4-6.8倍）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现：\n\n1. **Redis是根因服务**：Redis的HGET和HMSET操作延迟异常显著，延迟倍数高达22.7倍，这是最严重的延迟问题。\n\n2. **AdService严重延迟**：Frontend调用AdService的延迟问题非常普遍（出现38次），延迟倍数5.5-6.9倍。\n\n3. **下游服务受影响**：由于Redis延迟，依赖Redis的CartService出现连锁反应，进而影响Checkout流程。\n\n4. **ShippingService轻微延迟**：虽然延迟倍数较高，但绝对延迟值相对较小。\n\n**建议下一步**：深入分析Redis和AdService的具体错误日志，确认是否存在连接池耗尽、内存压力或网络分区等问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。让我分析异常指标并识别显著的故障模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.01飙升到0.6（变化率193%），同时rrt和rrt_max显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.01→0.6 (193%), rrt: 3438→13924 (121%), rrt_max: 43028→97818 (78%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.0飙升到0.6（变化率200%），rrt_max大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.0→0.6 (200%), rrt_max: 43046→86549 (67%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.0飙升到0.6（变化率200%），rrt和rrt_max显著恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.0→0.6 (200%), rrt: 5765→8730 (41%), rrt_max: 42729→88707 (70%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio出现异常，p99变化率200%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99: 0.0→18.22 (200%), client_error_ratio p99: 0.0→18.22 (200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，p99变化率200%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99: 0.0→15.87 (200%), client_error_ratio p99: 0.0→15.87 (200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes显著减少，node_cpu_usage_rate增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 12.5G→8.7G (36%减少), node_cpu_usage_rate: 34%→42% (21%增加)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max p99值大幅增加，从8877飙升至52292\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99: 8877→52292 (142%增加)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n通过初始扫描，我发现了以下关键异常：\n\n**主要发现：**\n1. **Adservice服务全面故障**：所有3个Pod（adservice-0、adservice-1、adservice-2）的CPU使用率都出现大幅飙升，同时响应时间显著恶化。\n\n2. **Cartservice错误率异常**：cartservice-1和cartservice-2出现错误率异常，p99错误率变化率达到200%。\n\n3. **节点资源压力**：aiops-k8s-08节点内存可用量减少36%，CPU使用率增加21%。\n\n4. **Emailservice性能问题**：emailservice-2的最大响应时间p99值出现142%的大幅增加。\n\n这些发现表明可能存在级联故障，从adservice的性能问题开始，影响到cartservice的错误率，并最终对节点资源造成压力。需要进一步深入分析这些组件之间的依赖关系。"}
